Global Bar & Grill strives to establish itself as the local leader in casual dining for families and truck drivers. Our globally influenced menu features an American taste with an international
flare. Some of our fan favorites include our tropical Calypso Shrimp appetizer and our authentic, Florida-born Cubano Sandwich. We take pride in our dishes, our staff, and the artistry that happens behind our kitchen doors.
We are entirely dedicated to providing our guests with highest quality experience, from the finest cuisine to extraordinary service and hospitality. We can’t wait to see you at our
extraordinary landmark.
